headline: Garmin advances dive safety technology with revolutionary Descent S1 Smart Buoy
summary: /July 15, 2025/PR Newswire – Garmin (NYSE: GRMN) today announced the Descent™ S1 Buoy, a revolutionary addition to the Garmin dive lineup that helps strengthen diver communication and enhances peace of mind for divers and crew.
